high_descs: turn left and walk to the end of the kitchen island on the left, then turn left and walk over to the middle of the kitchen counter on the right
grab the back side apple off of the kitchen counter there
turn left and walk over to the fridge on the right side of the room
place the apple inside of the fridge, cool it off in there for a bit, then take it back out
turn right and walk over to the microwave at the end of the room on the left side on top of the kitchen counter
place the apple inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a cooled off apple inside of the kitchen microwave

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen counter in front of the plate.
Grab a tomato from the counter.
Go to the fridge on your right.
Place the tomato in the fridge, then remove it.
Walk to the microwave on your right.
Place the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a tomato in the fridge and heat it again.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left around the kitchen island to walk to the two apples on the counter.
Pick up the apple directly behind the other apple on the counter.
Turn left to walk to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the freezer, removing it afterwards.
Make a right to walk across the room the the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill an apple to put it in the microwave.
